          "settings": {
            "icon": "<?xml version=\"1.0\" standalone=\"no\"?>\n\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" id=\"body_2\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\">\n\n<g transform=\"matrix(1.3333334 0 0 1.3333334 0 0)\">\n    <image x=\"0\" y=\"0\" xlink:href=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"75%\" height=\"75%\"></image>\n</g>\n</svg>",
            "title": "90 Days Money Back Guarantee",
            "content": "No-Hassle 100% Money-Back Guarantee!",
            "content_popup": "<h3>Returns Policy</h3>\n<p>We have a 90-day return policy, which means you can apply for a return within 90 days of receiving the item.</p>\n<p>Non-Returnable Items: Used, Clearance, promotional, or custom-made items (unless defective), Return requests made after 90 days.</p>\n<p>If there is no quality problem, you need to bear the return cost yourself.</p>\n<p>To initiate a return, you can contact us at support@reibii.com. If your return is accepted, we will send you a specific return shipping label(only supported by FedEx) and instructions on how and where to send the package.</p>"
          }
        },
