        "display_custom_tab_1": true,
        "custom_tab_title_1": "DETAILS",
        "custom_tab_content_1": "<p> </p>\n<h3>Specifications</h3>\n<p>Color: Black</p>\n<p>Material: Metal, PU</p>\n<p>Mounting Type: Freestanding</p>\n<p>Style: Modern</p>\n<p>Item Weight: 32.4 Pounds</p>\n<p>Item Dimensions: 36.2\"W X 15.8\"D X 46\"H</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Package Includes</h3>\n<p>1 x Laundry Sorter</p>\n<p>1 x Instruction</p>",
        "display_custom_tab_2": false,
        "custom_tab_title_2": "",
        "custom_tab_content_2": "",
        "display_custom_tab_3": true,
        "custom_tab_title_3": "faq",
        "custom_tab_content_3": "<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: Are the bags washable?</h3>\n<p>Sure. You can easily remove them from the sorter, soak them in cold water for ten minutes, then hand wash. Note: Please do not use bleach and fabric softener, do not iron and expose to the sun.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: What's the size of this laundry sorter?</h3>\n<p>Laundry Sorter with Shelves Dimensions: 36.2\"W X 15.8\"D X 46\"H, Laundry Bag:8.7”W X 14.2“D X 21.7”H.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: How can I get assembly instructions?</h3>\n<p>Each item comes with a paper instruction. If you need an electronic version, please feel free to <a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/contact\"><u>contact us</u></a>.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: Is it easy to install?</h3>\n<p>Yes, the installation is easy and can be completed independently within 10 minutes.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: How do I pay for my purchase?</h3>\n<p>You can pay by credit card or PayPal.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: How do I change or cancel my order after I've placed it?</h3>\n<p>In-stock items normally ship within 2 business days after an order has been placed. Before delivery, you can <a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/contact\"><u>contact us</u></a> to change the delivery information or cancel the order at any time. Once an item has shipped, change & cancellation are impossible.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: Do you ship to Alaska?</h3>\n<p>Only ship to 48 contiguous states and Washington D.C. within the US, excluding Alaska, Hawaii and Puerto Rico.</p>\n<p>Please refer to <a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/shipping-and-delivery\"><u>https://reibii.com/pages/shipping-and-delivery</u></a> for specific shipping policies.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Q: How is the shipping cost calculated?</h3>\n<p>Free shipping on all items.</p>",
        "display_custom_tab_4": false,
        "custom_tab_title_4": "",
        "custom_tab_content_4": "",
        "display_custom_tab_5": true,
        "custom_tab_title_5": "Shipping & Returns",
        "custom_tab_content_5": "<h3 data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Delivery</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Free shipping on all items in the REIBII online store.</li>\n<li>After you place your order, we will process your order within 2 working days.</li>\n<li>Typically, shipping time is expected to be 3-8 business days, and your order will be delivered to your doorstep by a third-party provider (e.g. FedEx, UPS) to the address you provide.</li>\n<li>When the package arrives, we will send you an arrival email to remind you, or you can check the shipping status of your order on the responsible shipping company's website.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong>Notice</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Currently, we only ship to the continental US; we do not ship to Alaska, Hawaii, or Puerto Rico.</li>\n<li>Please refer to <span style=\"color: #00aaff;\"><a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/shipping-and-delivery\" style=\"color: #00aaff;\">https://reibii.com/pages/shipping-and-delivery</a></span> for specific shipping policies.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Returns & Exchanges</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Time</strong> We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee, which means you can request a return within 30 days of receiving the item.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Request</strong> The item you send back must be in the same condition as the item you received, unworn or unused, labelled, and in its original packaging.</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Fee</strong> If the product has no quality problems, you must bear the return and exchange fees yourself.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Damage & Problems</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>If you receive a defective, incorrect or incomplete item, please<span style=\"color: #00aaff;\"> <a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/contact\" style=\"color: #00aaff;\">contact us</a></span> immediately and attach a photo of the damaged product (if applicable) so that we can promptly re-issue you a good product or refund you.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><strong>Notice</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Please keep all items and packaging materials until your claim is resolved. For a specific return policy, please refer to <span style=\"color: #00aaff;\"><a href=\"https://reibii.com/pages/return-refund-policy\" style=\"color: #00aaff;\">https://reibii.com/pages/return-policy</a></span>\n</li>\n</ul>",
        "display_custom_tab_6": true,
        "custom_tab_title_6": "Recommendations",
